{
  "stem": "10119.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they needed the powder for the munition.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there were three shifts working that every eight hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and our shift was-- our shift was, was at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us there by, by truck, open truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came back-- whoever came back was black from the dust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we used to make fun of the people when we went in the morning to work and they were coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where did you work?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were black, which forget about showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you were able to get washed up, you were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the people who worked at night were sleeping in the daytime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave us-- they gave us lots of soup when we came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They gave you soup?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave us soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The portion usually was soup and like two slices of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was your da-- your daily allowance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if you ate up the soup and the bread for the day, you didn't eat nothing till the next 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you were satisfied with the soup, save the bread-- if they didn't steal it from you overnight.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when you put it under your pillow, you didn't have anything that [? stopped ?] people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was lucky, because we had bunks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had bunks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at nights, while I was working, somebody else sleeped-- slept in it, which-- Oh.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a bunk for yourself?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a bunk for myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were like the three tiered bunks, one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and you had a bunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when, when one the girls-- when I was working, she slept in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when she was working, I slept in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't have our own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the same bunk, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
